Package: laserize
Type: Package
Title: Obtain LASER text emebeddings by interfacing the Python laserembeddings module
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Hauke", "Licht", email = "hauke.licht@uzh.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package provides an R interface to the sentence embedding functionality
    provided by the laserembeddings Python module.
    It projects texts from different languages onto the same, multilingual embedding space.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    reticulate,
Suggests: 
    testthat,
    mockery,
    tibble,
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
